WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
On a cold night, Hamlet sees his father's ghost
and learns a terrible secret.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Hamlet feels deep grief and doubt,
and he cannot decide how to act.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Hamlet pretends to be mad while he watches
the king for signs of guilt.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
A play at court mirrors the murder,
and Claudius reacts with sudden fear.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Rejected and heartbroken, Ophelia loses her peace
and slowly falls into despair.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
In the graveyard, Hamlet holds a skull
and thinks about death and time.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
The final duel begins, but poison and revenge
soon destroy the royal court.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.000
After great loss and silence, Hamlet dies,
and Denmark faces a tragic end.
